{"id":147376,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/叙利亚当局继续对起义民众施暴/","date":"2011-04-25T11:30:17Z","modified":"2011-04-25T11:30:17Z","title":"叙利亚当局继续对起义民众施暴","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大马士革</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">叙利亚政府军坦克周一（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）开进南部城市德拉（</span><span>Daraa</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）。据反对派称，至少已有</span><span>20</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人被军队杀害。反政府运动通过“脸书”报告说，安全力量还在杜马（</span><span>Duma</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）市的大量民宅内进行大规模搜查。达拉是反巴希尔·阿萨德总统起义运动的中心之一。数星期以来，叙利亚当局一直试图通过暴力和抓捕，终结反抗运动。人权组织称，迄今，当局暴力已导致至少</span><span>400</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人丧生。在其他阿拉伯国家民众革命的鼓舞下，叙利亚国内</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周前兴起要求民主改革浪潮，在发生多人遭枪杀事件后，示威者已要求推翻现政权。</span><span>2000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年上台执政至今的巴希尔·阿萨德总统数天前宣布将进行多项改革。另据报道，约旦一名高级外交官今天通报说，叙利亚方面已关闭两国之间的边界通道。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15027997%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E5%AF%B9%E8%B5%B7%E4%B9%89%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E6%96%BD%E6%9A%B4\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?